---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy">
  <article style="max-width: var(--measure); margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Geo-Traveller is a personal travel journal. This page describes what data the site collects.</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>The site is a static site served from Cloudflare's CDN. We do not run a server-side database, set tracking cookies, or collect personal information from visitors.</p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>If analytics is enabled, we use privacy-friendly analytics that collect aggregate visit counts only — no IP addresses, no fingerprinting, no cookies.</p>

    <h2>Comments and newsletter</h2>
    <p>If you choose to leave a comment (via Giscus, backed by GitHub Discussions) or subscribe to the email newsletter, the respective third party — GitHub or the newsletter provider — handles your data per their own privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Use the <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
